Package: socmixmods
Type: Package
Title: Fitting Binomial Mixture Models to Social Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Michael", "Weiss", email = "myemailaddress@weiss.com", role = c("aut")),
    person("Samuel", "Ellis", email = "samellisq@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: A package to fit k component binomial mixture models to 
    social association data. Fitted binomial mixture models can be used
    to assess social complexity (e.g Weiss et al. ...) or categorise
    social bonds (e.g. Ellis et al... UPCOMING). Package provides functions
    to fit and assess the fit of k-component mixture models. It also provides
    other related functions likely to be of use when working with mixture 
    models of on social data. Based on alogrithins described in Weiss et al ...
